This one shouldn't be renamed: the others have names following https://leanprover-community.github.io/contribute/naming.html, and this one did too, whereas the suggested change here breaks this convention.

```suggestion
theorem case_strong_induction_on [DecidableEq Œ±] {p : Finset Œ± ‚Üí Prop} (s : Finset Œ±) (h‚ÇÄ : p ‚àÖ)
```
